{"surah":{"number":51,"name":"الذاريات","englishName":"Adh-Dhariyat","englishTranslation":"The Winnowing Winds","ayahCount":60},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:14.605Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"By those [winds] scattering [dust] dispersing","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلذَّٰرِيَـٰتِ","english":"By those scattering","translit":"wal-dhāriyāti","root":"ذرو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ذَرْوًۭا","english":"dispersing","translit":"dharwan","root":"ذرو"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And those [clouds] carrying a load [of water]","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱلْحَـٰمِلَـٰتِ","english":"And those carrying","translit":"fal-ḥāmilāti","root":"حمل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وِقْرًۭا","english":"a load","translit":"wiq'ran","root":"وقر"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And those [ships] sailing with ease","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱلْجَـٰرِيَـٰتِ","english":"And those sailing","translit":"fal-jāriyāti","root":"جري"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يُسْرًۭا","english":"(with) ease","translit":"yus'ran","root":"يسر"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And those [angels] apportioning [each] matter,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱلْمُقَسِّمَـٰتِ","english":"And those distributing","translit":"fal-muqasimāti","root":"قسم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَمْرًا","english":"Command","translit":"amran","root":"أمر"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"Indeed, what you are promised is true.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","english":"Indeed, what","translit":"innamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُوعَدُونَ","english":"you are promised","translit":"tūʿadūna","root":"وعد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَصَادِقٌۭ","english":"(is) surely true","translit":"laṣādiqun","root":"صدق"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"And indeed, the recompense is to occur.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","english":"And indeed","translit":"wa-inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلدِّينَ","english":"the Judgment","translit":"l-dīna","root":"دين"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَوَٰقِعٌۭ","english":"(is) surely to occur","translit":"lawāqiʿun","root":"وقع"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"By the heaven containing pathways,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ","english":"By the heaven","translit":"wal-samāi","root":"سمو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ذَاتِ","english":"full of","translit":"dhāti","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْحُبُكِ","english":"pathways","translit":"l-ḥubuki","root":"حبك"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"Indeed, you are in differing speech.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّكُمْ","english":"Indeed, you","translit":"innakum","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَفِى","english":"(are) surely in","translit":"lafī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَوْلٍۢ","english":"a speech","translit":"qawlin","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُّخْتَلِفٍۢ","english":"differing","translit":"mukh'talifin","root":"خلف"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"Deluded away from the Qur'an is he who is deluded.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يُؤْفَكُ","english":"Deluded away","translit":"yu'faku","root":"أفك"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَنْهُ","english":"from it","translit":"ʿanhu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"(is he) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أُفِكَ","english":"is deluded","translit":"ufika","root":"أفك"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"Destroyed are the falsifiers","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُتِلَ","english":"Cursed be","translit":"qutila","root":"قتل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْخَرَّٰصُونَ","english":"the liars","translit":"l-kharāṣūna","root":"خرص"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"Who are within a flood [of confusion] and heedless.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"Those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"[they]","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(are) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"غَمْرَةٍۢ","english":"flood","translit":"ghamratin","root":"غمر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"سَاهُونَ","english":"(of) heedlessness","translit":"sāhūna","root":"سهو"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"They ask, \"When is the Day of Recompense?\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَسْـَٔلُونَ","english":"They ask","translit":"yasalūna","root":"سأل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَيَّانَ","english":"When","translit":"ayyāna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is the) Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلدِّينِ","english":"(of) Judgment","translit":"l-dīni","root":"دين"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"[It is] the Day they will be tormented over the Fire","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"A Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"they","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"over","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ","english":"the Fire","translit":"l-nāri","root":"نور"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يُفْتَنُونَ","english":"will be tried","translit":"yuf'tanūna","root":"فتن"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"[And will be told], \"Taste your torment. This is that for which you were impatient.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ذُوقُوا۟","english":"Taste","translit":"dhūqū","root":"ذوق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِتْنَتَكُمْ","english":"your trial","translit":"fit'natakum","root":"فتن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"This","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"(is) what","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كُنتُم","english":"you were","translit":"kuntum","root":"كون"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"for it","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"تَسْتَعْجِلُونَ","english":"seeking to hasten","translit":"tastaʿjilūna","root":"عجل"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"Indeed, the righteous will be among gardens and springs,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَّقِينَ","english":"the righteous","translit":"l-mutaqīna","root":"وقي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(will be) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتٍۢ","english":"Gardens","translit":"jannātin","root":"جنن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَعُيُونٍ","english":"and springs","translit":"waʿuyūnin","root":"عين"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"Accepting what their Lord has given them. Indeed, they were before that doers of good.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ءَاخِذِينَ","english":"Taking","translit":"ākhidhīna","root":"أخذ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَاتَىٰهُمْ","english":"their Lord has given them","translit":"ātāhum","root":"أتي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَبُّهُمْ ۚ","english":"their Lord has given them","translit":"rabbuhum","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ","english":"Indeed, they","translit":"innahum","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_016_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"were","translit":"kānū","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/051_016_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"قَبْلَ","english":"before","translit":"qabla","root":"قبل","audio":"wbw/051_016_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_016_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مُحْسِنِينَ","english":"good-doers","translit":"muḥ'sinīna","root":"حسن","audio":"wbw/051_016_010.mp3"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"They used to sleep but little of the night,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"They used to","translit":"kānū","root":"كون"},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَلِيلًۭا","english":"little","translit":"qalīlan","root":"قلل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّيْلِ","english":"the night","translit":"al-layli","root":"ليل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَا","english":"[what]","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَهْجَعُونَ","english":"sleep","translit":"yahjaʿūna","root":"هجع"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"And in the hours before dawn they would ask forgiveness,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَبِٱلْأَسْحَارِ","english":"And in the hours before dawn","translit":"wabil-asḥāri","root":"سحر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"they","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَسْتَغْفِرُونَ","english":"would ask forgiveness","translit":"yastaghfirūna","root":"غفر"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"And from their properties was [given] the right of the [needy] petitioner and the deprived.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفِىٓ","english":"And in","translit":"wafī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَمْوَٰلِهِمْ","english":"their wealth","translit":"amwālihim","root":"مول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَقٌّۭ","english":"(was the) right","translit":"ḥaqqun","root":"حقق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِّلسَّآئِلِ","english":"(of) those who asked","translit":"lilssāili","root":"سأل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَحْرُومِ","english":"and the deprived","translit":"wal-maḥrūmi","root":"حرم"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"And on the earth are signs for the certain [in faith]","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفِى","english":"And in","translit":"wafī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتٌۭ","english":"(are) signs","translit":"āyātun","root":"أيي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِّلْمُوقِنِينَ","english":"for those who are certain","translit":"lil'mūqinīna","root":"يقن"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"And in yourselves. Then will you not see?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفِىٓ","english":"And in","translit":"wafī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَنفُسِكُمْ ۚ","english":"yourselves","translit":"anfusikum","root":"نفس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَفَلَا","english":"Then will not","translit":"afalā","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_021_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُبْصِرُونَ","english":"you see","translit":"tub'ṣirūna","root":"بصر","audio":"wbw/051_021_005.mp3"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"And in the heaven is your provision and whatever you are promised.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفِى","english":"And in","translit":"wafī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءِ","english":"the heaven","translit":"l-samāi","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رِزْقُكُمْ","english":"(is) your provision","translit":"riz'qukum","root":"رزق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and what","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تُوعَدُونَ","english":"you are promised","translit":"tūʿadūna","root":"وعد"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"Then by the Lord of the heaven and earth, indeed, it is truth - just as [sure as] it is that you are speaking.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَوَرَبِّ","english":"Then by (the) Lord","translit":"fawarabbi","root":"ربب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءِ","english":"(of) the heaven","translit":"l-samāi","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"indeed, it","translit":"innahu","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَحَقٌّۭ","english":"(is) surely (the) truth","translit":"laḥaqqun","root":"حقق"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِّثْلَ","english":"(just) as","translit":"mith'la","root":"مثل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"[what]","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَنَّكُمْ","english":"you","translit":"annakum","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"تَنطِقُونَ","english":"speak","translit":"tanṭiqūna","root":"نطق"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"Has there reached you the story of the honored guests of Abraham? -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَلْ","english":"Has","translit":"hal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَتَىٰكَ","english":"reached you","translit":"atāka","root":"أتي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَدِيثُ","english":"(the) narration","translit":"ḥadīthu","root":"حدث"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ضَيْفِ","english":"(of the) guests","translit":"ḍayfi","root":"ضيف"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِبْرَٰهِيمَ","english":"(of) Ibrahim","translit":"ib'rāhīma","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمُكْرَمِينَ","english":"the honored","translit":"l-muk'ramīna","root":"كرم"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"When they entered upon him and said, \"[We greet you with] peace.\" He answered, \"[And upon you] peace, [you are] a people unknown.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"When","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"دَخَلُوا۟","english":"they entered","translit":"dakhalū","root":"دخل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","english":"upon him","translit":"ʿalayhi","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَقَالُوا۟","english":"and said","translit":"faqālū","root":"قول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"سَلَـٰمًۭا ۖ","english":"Peace","translit":"salāman","root":"سلم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"قَالَ","english":"He said","translit":"qāla","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/051_025_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"سَلَـٰمٌۭ","english":"Peace","translit":"salāmun","root":"سلم","audio":"wbw/051_025_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"قَوْمٌۭ","english":"a people","translit":"qawmun","root":"قوم","audio":"wbw/051_025_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مُّنكَرُونَ","english":"unknown","translit":"munkarūna","root":"نكر","audio":"wbw/051_025_010.mp3"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"Then he went to his family and came with a fat [roasted] calf","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَرَاغَ","english":"Then he went","translit":"farāgha","root":"روغ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَىٰٓ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَهْلِهِۦ","english":"his household","translit":"ahlihi","root":"أهل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَجَآءَ","english":"and came","translit":"fajāa","root":"جيأ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِعِجْلٍۢ","english":"with a calf","translit":"biʿij'lin","root":"عجل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"سَمِينٍۢ","english":"fat","translit":"samīnin","root":"سمن"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"And placed it near them; he said, \"Will you not eat?\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَقَرَّبَهُۥٓ","english":"And he placed it near","translit":"faqarrabahu","root":"قرب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِمْ","english":"[to] them","translit":"ilayhim","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَالَ","english":"he said","translit":"qāla","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَلَا","english":"Will not","translit":"alā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَأْكُلُونَ","english":"you eat","translit":"takulūna","root":"أكل"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"And he felt from them apprehension. They said, \"Fear not,\" and gave him good tidings of a learned boy.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَوْجَسَ","english":"Then he felt","translit":"fa-awjasa","root":"وجس"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْهُمْ","english":"from them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"خِيفَةًۭ ۖ","english":"a fear","translit":"khīfatan","root":"خوف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","english":"They said","translit":"qālū","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/051_028_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(Do) not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_028_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"تَخَفْ ۖ","english":"fear","translit":"takhaf","root":"خوف","audio":"wbw/051_028_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَبَشَّرُوهُ","english":"and they gave him glad tidings","translit":"wabasharūhu","root":"بشر","audio":"wbw/051_028_009.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِغُلَـٰمٍ","english":"of a son","translit":"bighulāmin","root":"غلم","audio":"wbw/051_028_010.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"عَلِيمٍۢ","english":"learned","translit":"ʿalīmin","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/051_028_011.mp3"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"And his wife approached with a cry [of alarm] and struck her face and said, \"[I am] a barren old woman!\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَقْبَلَتِ","english":"Then came forward","translit":"fa-aqbalati","root":"قبل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱمْرَأَتُهُۥ","english":"his wife","translit":"im'ra-atuhu","root":"مرأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"with","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"صَرَّةٍۢ","english":"a loud voice","translit":"ṣarratin","root":"صرر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَصَكَّتْ","english":"and struck","translit":"faṣakkat","root":"صكك"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَجْهَهَا","english":"her face","translit":"wajhahā","root":"وجه"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَقَالَتْ","english":"and she said","translit":"waqālat","root":"قول"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَجُوزٌ","english":"An old woman","translit":"ʿajūzun","root":"عجز"},{"position":9,"arabic":"عَقِيمٌۭ","english":"barren","translit":"ʿaqīmun","root":"عقم"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"They said, \"Thus has said your Lord; indeed, He is the Wise, the Knowing.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","english":"They said","translit":"qālū","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكِ","english":"Thus","translit":"kadhāliki","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَالَ","english":"said","translit":"qāla","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَبُّكِ ۖ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbuki","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"Indeed, He","translit":"innahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_030_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"[He]","translit":"huwa","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_030_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْحَكِيمُ","english":"(is) the All-Wise","translit":"l-ḥakīmu","root":"حكم","audio":"wbw/051_030_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْعَلِيمُ","english":"the All-Knower","translit":"l-ʿalīmu","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/051_030_009.mp3"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"[Abraham] said, \"Then what is your business [here], O messengers?\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"۞ قَالَ","english":"He said","translit":"qāla","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/051_031_002.mp3"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَمَا","english":"Then what","translit":"famā","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_031_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"خَطْبُكُمْ","english":"(is) your mission","translit":"khaṭbukum","root":"خطب","audio":"wbw/051_031_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَيُّهَا","english":"O messengers","translit":"ayyuhā","root":"أيي","audio":"wbw/051_031_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمُرْسَلُونَ","english":"O messengers","translit":"l-mur'salūna","root":"رسل","audio":"wbw/051_031_006.mp3"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"They said, \"Indeed, we have been sent to a people of criminals","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","english":"They said","translit":"qālū","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","english":"Indeed, we","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أُرْسِلْنَآ","english":"[we] have been sent","translit":"ur'sil'nā","root":"رسل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"قَوْمٍۢ","english":"a people","translit":"qawmin","root":"قوم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مُّجْرِمِينَ","english":"criminal","translit":"muj'rimīna","root":"جرم"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"To send down upon them stones of clay,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِنُرْسِلَ","english":"That we may send down","translit":"linur'sila","root":"رسل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"upon them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"حِجَارَةًۭ","english":"stones","translit":"ḥijāratan","root":"حجر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"طِينٍۢ","english":"clay","translit":"ṭīnin","root":"طين"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"Marked in the presence of your Lord for the transgressors.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مُّسَوَّمَةً","english":"Marked","translit":"musawwamatan","root":"سوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عِندَ","english":"by your Lord","translit":"ʿinda","root":"عند"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"by your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِلْمُسْرِفِينَ","english":"for the transgressors","translit":"lil'mus'rifīna","root":"سرف"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"So We brought out whoever was in the cities of the believers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَخْرَجْنَا","english":"Then We brought out","translit":"fa-akhrajnā","root":"خرج"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَن","english":"(those) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"were","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","english":"the believers","translit":"l-mu'minīna","root":"أمن"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"And We found not within them other than a [single] house of Muslims.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَمَا","english":"But not","translit":"famā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَجَدْنَا","english":"We found","translit":"wajadnā","root":"وجد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"غَيْرَ","english":"other than","translit":"ghayra","root":"غير"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَيْتٍۢ","english":"a house","translit":"baytin","root":"بيت"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْمُسْلِمِينَ","english":"the Muslims","translit":"l-mus'limīna","root":"سلم"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"And We left therein a sign for those who fear the painful punishment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَتَرَكْنَا","english":"And We left","translit":"wataraknā","root":"ترك"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِيهَآ","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَايَةًۭ","english":"a Sign","translit":"āyatan","root":"أيي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِّلَّذِينَ","english":"for those who","translit":"lilladhīna","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَخَافُونَ","english":"fear","translit":"yakhāfūna","root":"خوف"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْعَذَابَ","english":"the punishment","translit":"l-ʿadhāba","root":"عذب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَلِيمَ","english":"the painful","translit":"l-alīma","root":"ألم"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"And in Moses [was a sign], when We sent him to Pharaoh with clear authority.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفِى","english":"And in","translit":"wafī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مُوسَىٰٓ","english":"Musa","translit":"mūsā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"when","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَـٰهُ","english":"We sent him","translit":"arsalnāhu","root":"رسل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"فِرْعَوْنَ","english":"Firaun","translit":"fir'ʿawna","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"بِسُلْطَـٰنٍۢ","english":"with an authority","translit":"bisul'ṭānin","root":"سلط"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مُّبِينٍۢ","english":"clear","translit":"mubīnin","root":"بين"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"But he turned away with his supporters and said,\" A magician or a madman.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَتَوَلَّىٰ","english":"But he turned away","translit":"fatawallā","root":"ولي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِرُكْنِهِۦ","english":"with his supporters","translit":"biruk'nihi","root":"ركن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","english":"and said","translit":"waqāla","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَـٰحِرٌ","english":"A magician","translit":"sāḥirun","root":"سحر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَوْ","english":"or","translit":"aw","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَجْنُونٌۭ","english":"a madman","translit":"majnūnun","root":"جنن"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"So We took him and his soldiers and cast them into the sea, and he was blameworthy.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَخَذْنَـٰهُ","english":"So We took him","translit":"fa-akhadhnāhu","root":"أخذ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَجُنُودَهُۥ","english":"and his hosts","translit":"wajunūdahu","root":"جند"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَنَبَذْنَـٰهُمْ","english":"and threw them","translit":"fanabadhnāhum","root":"نبذ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","english":"into","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْيَمِّ","english":"the sea","translit":"l-yami","root":"يمم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","english":"while he","translit":"wahuwa","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُلِيمٌۭ","english":"(was) blameworthy","translit":"mulīmun","root":"لوم"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"And in 'Aad [was a sign], when We sent against them the barren wind.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفِى","english":"And in","translit":"wafī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَادٍ","english":"Aad","translit":"ʿādin","root":"عود"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"when","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَا","english":"We sent","translit":"arsalnā","root":"رسل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمُ","english":"against them","translit":"ʿalayhimu","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلرِّيحَ","english":"the wind","translit":"l-rīḥa","root":"روح"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْعَقِيمَ","english":"the barren","translit":"l-ʿaqīma","root":"عقم"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"It left nothing of what it came upon but that it made it like disintegrated ruins.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَا","english":"Not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَذَرُ","english":"it left","translit":"tadharu","root":"وذر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَتَتْ","english":"it came","translit":"atat","root":"أتي"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","english":"upon it","translit":"ʿalayhi","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"but","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"جَعَلَتْهُ","english":"it made it","translit":"jaʿalathu","root":"جعل"},{"position":9,"arabic":"كَٱلرَّمِيمِ","english":"like disintegrated ruins","translit":"kal-ramīmi","root":"رمم"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"And in Thamud, when it was said to them, \"Enjoy yourselves for a time.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفِى","english":"And in","translit":"wafī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ثَمُودَ","english":"Thamud","translit":"thamūda","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"when","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"قِيلَ","english":"was said","translit":"qīla","root":"قول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"to them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"تَمَتَّعُوا۟","english":"Enjoy (yourselves)","translit":"tamattaʿū","root":"متع"},{"position":7,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","english":"for","translit":"ḥattā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"حِينٍۢ","english":"a time","translit":"ḥīnin","root":"حين"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"But they were insolent toward the command of their Lord, so the thunderbolt seized them while they were looking on.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَعَتَوْا۟","english":"But they rebelled","translit":"faʿataw","root":"عتو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَنْ","english":"against","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَمْرِ","english":"(the) Command","translit":"amri","root":"أمر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ","english":"(of) their Lord","translit":"rabbihim","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَأَخَذَتْهُمُ","english":"so seized them","translit":"fa-akhadhathumu","root":"أخذ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰعِقَةُ","english":"the thunderbolt","translit":"l-ṣāʿiqatu","root":"صعق"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","english":"while they","translit":"wahum","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَنظُرُونَ","english":"were looking","translit":"yanẓurūna","root":"نظر"}]},{"number":45,"translation":"And they were unable to arise, nor could they defend themselves.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَمَا","english":"Then not","translit":"famā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱسْتَطَـٰعُوا۟","english":"they were able to","translit":"is'taṭāʿū","root":"طوع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","english":"[of]","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"قِيَامٍۢ","english":"stand","translit":"qiyāmin","root":"قوم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"they could","translit":"kānū","root":"كون"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُنتَصِرِينَ","english":"help themselves","translit":"muntaṣirīna","root":"نصر"}]},{"number":46,"translation":"And [We destroyed] the people of Noah before; indeed, they were a people defiantly disobedient.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَوْمَ","english":"And (the) people","translit":"waqawma","root":"قوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"نُوحٍۢ","english":"(of) Nuh","translit":"nūḥin","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"before","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَبْلُ ۖ","english":"before","translit":"qablu","root":"قبل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ","english":"indeed, they","translit":"innahum","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_046_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"were","translit":"kānū","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/051_046_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"قَوْمًۭا","english":"a people","translit":"qawman","root":"قوم","audio":"wbw/051_046_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَـٰسِقِينَ","english":"defiantly disobedient","translit":"fāsiqīna","root":"فسق","audio":"wbw/051_046_009.mp3"}]},{"number":47,"translation":"And the heaven We constructed with strength, and indeed, We are [its] expander.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءَ","english":"And the heaven","translit":"wal-samāa","root":"سمو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَنَيْنَـٰهَا","english":"We constructed it","translit":"banaynāhā","root":"بني"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِأَيْي۟دٍۢ","english":"with strength","translit":"bi-aydin","root":"أيد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَإِنَّا","english":"and indeed, We","translit":"wa-innā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَمُوسِعُونَ","english":"(are) surely (its) Expanders","translit":"lamūsiʿūna","root":"وسع"}]},{"number":48,"translation":"And the earth We have spread out, and excellent is the preparer.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"And the earth","translit":"wal-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَرَشْنَـٰهَا","english":"We have spread it","translit":"farashnāhā","root":"فرش"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَنِعْمَ","english":"how excellent","translit":"faniʿ'ma","root":"نعم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَـٰهِدُونَ","english":"(are) the Spreaders","translit":"l-māhidūna","root":"مهد"}]},{"number":49,"translation":"And of all things We created two mates; perhaps you will remember.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمِن","english":"And of","translit":"wamin","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كُلِّ","english":"every","translit":"kulli","root":"كلل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَا","english":"We have created","translit":"khalaqnā","root":"خلق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"زَوْجَيْنِ","english":"pairs","translit":"zawjayni","root":"زوج"},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَعَلَّكُمْ","english":"so that you may","translit":"laʿallakum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"تَذَكَّرُونَ","english":"remember","translit":"tadhakkarūna","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":50,"translation":"So flee to Allah. Indeed, I am to you from Him a clear warner.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَفِرُّوٓا۟","english":"So flee","translit":"fafirrū","root":"فرر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۖ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِنِّى","english":"indeed, I am","translit":"innī","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_050_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَكُم","english":"to you","translit":"lakum","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_050_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِّنْهُ","english":"from Him","translit":"min'hu","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_050_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"نَذِيرٌۭ","english":"a warner","translit":"nadhīrun","root":"نذر","audio":"wbw/051_050_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مُّبِينٌۭ","english":"clear","translit":"mubīnun","root":"بين","audio":"wbw/051_050_009.mp3"}]},{"number":51,"translation":"And do not make [as equal] with Allah another deity. Indeed, I am to you from Him a clear warner.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And (do) not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَجْعَلُوا۟","english":"make","translit":"tajʿalū","root":"جعل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَعَ","english":"with","translit":"maʿa","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَـٰهًا","english":"god","translit":"ilāhan","root":"أله"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ءَاخَرَ ۖ","english":"another","translit":"ākhara","root":"أخر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِنِّى","english":"Indeed, I am","translit":"innī","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_051_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"لَكُم","english":"to you","translit":"lakum","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_051_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مِّنْهُ","english":"from Him","translit":"min'hu","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_051_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"نَذِيرٌۭ","english":"a warner","translit":"nadhīrun","root":"نذر","audio":"wbw/051_051_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"مُّبِينٌۭ","english":"clear","translit":"mubīnun","root":"بين","audio":"wbw/051_051_012.mp3"}]},{"number":52,"translation":"Similarly, there came not to those before them any messenger except that they said, \"A magician or a madman.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","english":"Likewise","translit":"kadhālika","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَتَى","english":"came","translit":"atā","root":"أتي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"(to) those","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","english":"before them","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"قَبْلِهِم","english":"before them","translit":"qablihim","root":"قبل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"رَّسُولٍ","english":"Messenger","translit":"rasūlin","root":"رسل"},{"position":9,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"but","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","english":"they said","translit":"qālū","root":"قول"},{"position":11,"arabic":"سَاحِرٌ","english":"A magician","translit":"sāḥirun","root":"سحر"},{"position":12,"arabic":"أَوْ","english":"or","translit":"aw","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"مَجْنُونٌ","english":"a madman","translit":"majnūnun","root":"جنن"}]},{"number":53,"translation":"Did they suggest it to them? Rather, they [themselves] are a transgressing people.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَتَوَاصَوْا۟","english":"Have they transmitted it to them","translit":"atawāṣaw","root":"وصي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِهِۦ ۚ","english":"Have they transmitted it to them","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بَلْ","english":"Nay","translit":"bal","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_053_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"they","translit":"hum","root":"","audio":"wbw/051_053_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"قَوْمٌۭ","english":"(are) a people","translit":"qawmun","root":"قوم","audio":"wbw/051_053_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"طَاغُونَ","english":"transgressing","translit":"ṭāghūna","root":"طغي","audio":"wbw/051_053_007.mp3"}]},{"number":54,"translation":"So leave them, [O Muhammad], for you are not to be blamed.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَتَوَلَّ","english":"So turn away","translit":"fatawalla","root":"ولي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَنْهُمْ","english":"from them","translit":"ʿanhum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَمَآ","english":"for not","translit":"famā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَنتَ","english":"you","translit":"anta","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِمَلُومٍۢ","english":"(are) to be blamed","translit":"bimalūmin","root":"لوم"}]},{"number":55,"translation":"And remind, for indeed, the reminder benefits the believers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَذَكِّرْ","english":"And remind","translit":"wadhakkir","root":"ذكر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","english":"for indeed","translit":"fa-inna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلذِّكْرَىٰ","english":"the reminder","translit":"l-dhik'rā","root":"ذكر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تَنفَعُ","english":"benefits","translit":"tanfaʿu","root":"نفع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","english":"the believers","translit":"l-mu'minīna","root":"أمن"}]},{"number":56,"translation":"And I did not create the jinn and mankind except to worship Me.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَلَقْتُ","english":"I have created","translit":"khalaqtu","root":"خلق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْجِنَّ","english":"the jinn","translit":"l-jina","root":"جنن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْإِنسَ","english":"and the mankind","translit":"wal-insa","root":"أنس"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"لِيَعْبُدُونِ","english":"that they worship Me","translit":"liyaʿbudūni","root":"عبد"}]},{"number":57,"translation":"I do not want from them any provision, nor do I want them to feed Me.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"Not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أُرِيدُ","english":"I want","translit":"urīdu","root":"رود"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِنْهُم","english":"from them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"رِّزْقٍۢ","english":"provision","translit":"riz'qin","root":"رزق"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَآ","english":"and not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"أُرِيدُ","english":"I want","translit":"urīdu","root":"رود"},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"يُطْعِمُونِ","english":"they (should) feed Me","translit":"yuṭ'ʿimūni","root":"طعم"}]},{"number":58,"translation":"Indeed, it is Allah who is the [continual] Provider, the firm possessor of strength.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"He","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلرَّزَّاقُ","english":"(is) the All-Provider","translit":"l-razāqu","root":"رزق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ذُو","english":"Possessor","translit":"dhū","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْقُوَّةِ","english":"(of) Power","translit":"l-quwati","root":"قوي"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْمَتِينُ","english":"the Strong","translit":"l-matīnu","root":"متن"}]},{"number":59,"translation":"And indeed, for those who have wronged is a portion [of punishment] like the portion of their predecessors, so let them not impatiently urge Me.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","english":"So indeed","translit":"fa-inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","english":"for those who","translit":"lilladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ظَلَمُوا۟","english":"do wrong","translit":"ẓalamū","root":"ظلم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذَنُوبًۭا","english":"(is) a portion","translit":"dhanūban","root":"ذنب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِّثْلَ","english":"like","translit":"mith'la","root":"مثل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ذَنُوبِ","english":"(the) portion","translit":"dhanūbi","root":"ذنب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبِهِمْ","english":"(of) their companions","translit":"aṣḥābihim","root":"صحب"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَلَا","english":"so let them not ask Me to hasten","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"يَسْتَعْجِلُونِ","english":"so let them not ask Me to hasten","translit":"yastaʿjilūni","root":"عجل"}]},{"number":60,"translation":"And woe to those who have disbelieved from their Day which they are promised.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَوَيْلٌۭ","english":"Then woe","translit":"fawaylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلَّذِينَ","english":"to those who","translit":"lilladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"disbelieve","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَوْمِهِمُ","english":"their Day","translit":"yawmihimu","root":"يوم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"which","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"يُوعَدُونَ","english":"they are promised","translit":"yūʿadūna","root":"وعد"}]}]}
